articles.title: T20 WC: Stoinis reveals turning point of game following Australia's win over Scotland - Hindustan Times
articles.description: Half-centuries from Travis Head and Marcus Stoinis helped Australia end the group stage unbeaten and defeated Scotland by five wickets in their ICC T20 World Cup match at Saint Lucia on Sunday. | Crickit
